{"tid":1632261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我要連登個個都要有獨立思考","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:04:13.000Z","uid":116775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"708784ad7c28e2085cc89176b1fab039748ebe09","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"由今日起，可唔可以啲comment 唔好淨係得幾隻字，喺咁屌人分化，5毛，帶風向就算。<br />\n唔喺唔比大家屌，但要都要言之有物啊。<br />\n要屌人嘅唔該要有point，唔好淨喺得幾隻字，手足們 唔該 睇曬啲comment 先好去落判斷。<br />\n唔好 喺唔喺 都推，跟大隊屌人，大個仔啦有多啲獨立思考能力啦。<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.hku.hk/~jwilam/reading/argument/argu_elements.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.hku.hk%2F~jwilam%2Freading%2Fargument%2Fargu_elements.htm&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=302e21dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.hku.hk/~jwilam/reading/argument/argu_elements.htm</a><br />\n要 屌人/同人討論 都要有說服力啊<br />\n如果個個淨喺識屌人分化，5毛，帶風向，咁就真係被分化，被帶風向啦。我唔想一個咁好嘅平台被人搞到咁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗"},{"pid":"c7f1a44c9b2802eba5b2105f975b010d692cbb4a","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6f9a3b1692429a9b1bcac1c99d03b80ae334f94","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffbd83653d7b1d246cb6b1262645af990e3d1797","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77b43ac2b376e563d4ec877b6fa38e49d1feedf4","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d7cec3cc9bb7b2d71db35ed32e4b5d0ceb7eca0","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ced6e316d0876ef50ce950cd108b71ea807c407","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb048725fb8b1db782ff9aa4eca01b5293ec600f","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0d26badd5f414557ee0df0ee5ecda570955f92c","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf739b9e3684dc80f7272f64bf4e9690cd802879","tid":1632261,"uid":142010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"e4b2dd2f9ff9596546d5cb1de518ec5db77f8e01","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"今日見到太多post 互屌，留comment 淨喺講一句分化撚，帶風向，喺幫唔到呢件事，我地要嘅喺連登咁多位手足嘅智慧啊。"},{"pid":"9da1304c2aec5e46c3cef070a762c0ea4453a8d4","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1029a536d4fc9dabc10d8d6e9fbb328b3527665","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a4541ef0b46b5fdf2b63789cb181617b463eb93","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"423ede0891bb56cbf8cf52240b6be1e295f6e9d6","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bd5b52e7906bb19b8d0e4ea37f7c614c8279f6a","tid":1632261,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa49008d68ce198fc45d6868a0776f7c6c2cfb0b","tid":1632261,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}